title: Converse CONS Project : London launch party with Pusha T, Krept N Konan and Sratcha DVA
description:
Pusha T, Krept N Konan and Scratcha DVA talk creativity and motivation at the CONS Project London launch party in Peckham, May 29th 2014.

For the full line-up and to apply for tickets to all CONS Project London events head to conversecons.com/ldn
